.TH eunit_surefire 3 "eunit 2.10.2" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
eunit_surefire \- Surefire reports for EUnit (Format used by Maven and Atlassian Bamboo for example to integrate test results). Based on initial code from Paul Guyot.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Example: Generate XML result file in the current directory:

.IP
.nf
     eunit:test([fib, eunit_examples],
                [{report,{eunit_surefire,[{dir,"."}]}}]).

.fi

.PP
\fISee also: \fR\fIeunit\fR.

.SH FUNCTIONS
.LP
